> Capo=4

<intro>
[Fmaj7][G][Em][A][Dm7][G6][C][C]

<verse 1>
[]当你|dang ni|When you are [C]老了 头发|lao le tou fa|old and grey and [Em]白了 睡|bai le shui|full of
[Fsus2]意 昏|yi hun|sleep, [G]沉 当你|chen dang ni|nodding; When you are [C]老了 走不|lao le zou bu|old and cannot
[Em]动了 炉火旁|dong le lu huo pang|move, by the fire [Fsus2]取暖 回忆|qu nuan hui yi|take your rest, dream of [G]青春|qing chun|youth

<chorus>
[Am]多少人|duo shao ren|How many [Em]曾爱你青春|ceng ai ni qing chun|loved your moments of [Fsus2]欢畅的|huan chang de|glad [C]时辰|shi chen|grace
[Dm7]爱慕你的美|ai mu ni de mei|And loved your beauty [G]丽 假意或|li jia yi huo|with love false or [C]真心|zhen xin|true [Cmaj7]
[Am]只有一个|zhi you yi ge|But one man [Em]人还爱你|ren hai ai ni|loved the [Fsus2]虔诚的灵|qian cheng de ling|pilgrim soul in you [Am]魂 爱|hun ai|And loved
[Dm7]你苍老的|ni cang lao de|the sorrows of your [G]脸上的|lian shang de|changing [C]皱纹|zhou wen|face

<verse 2>
