[Em]低垂|di chui|droop [Fsus2]灯火昏|deng huo hun|the lights are [G]黄不|huang bu|dim and [C]定 风吹|ding feng chui|unsteady; The wind blows
[Am]过来你的|guo lai ni de|news of you [Em]消息 这|xiao xi zhe|this [Fsus2]就是|jiu shi|is [G]我心里的|wo xin li de|the song in my heart
[C]歌|ge|song

